I believe that Art and Tom are out on personal business.  Also, there are those who have never misbehaved and really don't need to make a pledge.<br><br>
There is no shortage of Gung Ho attitude here and I feel no essence of cowardice.  What I do see is that defense mechanism, Splitting, &quot;all black or all white..no gray!&quot;<br><br>
We like all creatures must learn when to hold'em and when to fold'em.  If we choose to control the thoughts and actions of others, we must endeavor to gain that through persuasion, example, and academic leadership...not the rattling of swords.<br><br>
Our experiences and problems are common but there is a uniqueness about us that cries out to be shared.  From our personal diversities we provide broader perspectives.  A dim path is now well lit.  Lost souls can move closer to the camp!<br><br>
A silent jury shall decide if we are brilliant or foolish, strong or weak, practical or ridiculos..and we may never hear the verdict.<br><br>
